<div class="content-card">
<div class="dtpghdg">Wine Notes</div> <div class="list-row"> <div class="list-row-inner">
<div itemprop="description">
Petrus is not actually a 'chateau' per se, although it is often referred to as such. Ownership: Jean-Francois Moueix.
</div>
<div>
Price Range of 750ml bottle, ex-tax in EUR<br>
Average:
&#8364;4,148
&nbsp;&nbsp;From: &#8364;3,354
&nbsp;&nbsp;To: &#8364;5,730
<span itemprop="offers" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/AggregateOffer">
<meta itemprop="priceCurrency" content="EUR">
<meta itemprop="price" content="4148">
<meta itemprop="lowPrice" content="3354"> <meta itemprop="highPrice" content="5730">
<meta itemprop="offerCount" content="10">
</span>
